Dear Customer,
Please find attached a Price Catalogue (PRICAT) for items that you have on order but not yet supplied.:

'
.head 8 +  If fnEX_CustCreateFile( 0, nPricatCustNo, '', 'PRICAT', 0, dtPricatDate, hEX_PRICATFormatFile, spShortFileName, sSourceFile )
